quests.task:
Today you are going on a Kindness Hunt! üëÄüíñ
Look around the classroom, playground, or in a story we read and find an example of someone being kind.

Kindness can look like:
	‚Ä¢	Helping a friend pick up dropped pencils ‚úèÔ∏è
	‚Ä¢	Including someone in a game ‚öΩ
	‚Ä¢	Saying ‚Äúthank you‚Äù or giving a compliment üåü
	‚Ä¢	Sharing materials with a partner üñçÔ∏è

When you spot an act of kindness, describe what the person did and explain how it helped or made someone feel.

üëâ Your job is to be a kindness detective and report back on the good things you find!
